{"tid":428431,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"SONY A9鏡下的曹星如","createTime":"2017-10-08T05:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T10:25:32.000Z","uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4bff44dd37d24ac0d5480e1ff503faefe90a5d","tid":428431,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/130919_9552a4c0b6aab39cb1433a3476ed168d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F130919_9552a4c0b6aab39cb1433a3476ed168d.jpg&h=fc918aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：香港01<br />\n攝影：余俊亮<br />\n<br />\n引言<br />\n<br />\n眼睛腫了，賽後哭了、笑了、再哭了，最後，送醫院了。<br />\n這一夜，「王者對決3」，曹星如值得被記住的，就是這些。<br />\n他從沒在比賽後像孩子般嚎啕大哭，唯獨這一夜&mdash;&mdash;因為，他與河野公平的對決，走的每一步、出的每一拳、流的每滴汗，全都實實在在。<br />\n攝影：余俊亮，撰文：李思詠<br />\n器材：Sony A9相機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F/124284/-%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%8222%E6%88%B0-%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF-%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E6%8B%B3-%E9%82%A3%E8%A1%8C%E6%B7%9A-%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E4%BA%86%E5%AF%A6%E5%AF%A6%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%2583%258F%2F124284%2F-%25E6%259B%25B9%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25A6%258222%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E5%259C%2596%25E8%25BC%25AF-%25E9%2582%25A3%25E4%25BA%259B%25E6%258B%25B3-%25E9%2582%25A3%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25B7%259A-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259B%25B9%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25A6%2582&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=be390713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F/124284/-%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%8222%E6%88%B0-%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF-%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E6%8B%B3-%E9%82%A3%E8%A1%8C%E6%B7%9A-%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E4%BA%86%E5%AF%A6%E5%AF%A6%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%